description: Add a glow of mystic charm to your home with this decorative accent lamp that depicts Bigfoot flipping the bird and wanting to be left alone in the woods. Creatively crafted from metal from years of maintenance-free use, the hand-painted accents give it a unique charm that compliments a variety of home decor styles, from forest lodge & cabin to rustic Western Americana. Measuring 8 inches long, 4 inches deep, and 12.25 inches high; it uses two bulbs (included) and sports a 50-inch power cable with an in-line rotary switch for easy use in your living room, bedroom, bathroom, kitchen, home office, or study. Makes a great way to give a room some ambient light and style, or a fun gift for sasquatch-loving friends and family.
